## Stat Block Format

Files use Homebrewery blockquote format. Key fields:

- `{@atk mw}` = melee weapon attack
- `{@atk rw}` = ranged weapon attack  
- `{@hit N}` = +N to hit
- `{@h}` = *Hit:* (start of damage line)
- `{@damage NdN}` = damage dice
- `{@dc N}` = DC N
- `{@spell name}` = spell name
- `{@condition name}` = condition name

These tags render as plain text in Obsidian/your markdown viewer.
